metadata.name: VERNEINTES EUROPA
metadata.description:
NEGATED EUROPA // Europa, the consert of Zeus, our beloved colorful continent — and the union of peace, its values and the well-being of its citizens. When boosting its capabilities and resilience... Europa, you must not neglect engagement with the wider world, or do you? 
— 
My comeback genesis series drop, after 2 years absence of doing crypto art. 
•  Music: LITC-Type Beat by HoliznaCC0
